column1: IF ccr_thf_d is MF 1 AND ccr_zob_dhf_d is MF 0 THEN 4_Obese is MF 1 AND 1_SousPoid is MF 0 AND 5_ExtremeObese is MF 1
IF ccr_s_at_d is MF 1 AND ccr_sa_thb_d is MF 1 AND ccr_cortisol_d is MF 2 THEN 3_Surpoid is MF 0 AND 4_Obese is MF 0
IF ccr_thb_d is MF 1 AND ccr_testosterone_d is MF 0 THEN 4_Obese is MF 1 AND 2_Normal is MF 1
IF ccr_cortisone_d is MF 1 AND ccr_testosterone_d is MF 0 THEN 2_Normal is MF 1 AND 1_SousPoid is MF 0 AND 5_ExtremeObese is MF 0
IF ccr_ll_oxo_etio_d is MF 0 AND ccr_testosterone_d is MF 1 THEN 1_SousPoid is MF 1 AND 4_Obese is MF 0 AND 5_ExtremeObese is MF 0
ELSE : 1_SousPoid is 1  2_Normal is 0  3_Surpoid is 0  4_Obese is 0  5_ExtremeObese is 0
